                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "The given request was invalid. This can be caused by a number of things:\n  * The given URL was not found.\n  * The given URL is not a streaming URL (i.e. it does not return a chunked response).\n  * The given URL does not return a JSON data type.\n\nThe response body contains a list of URLs that were not valid.\n",
